Name: Stitches two string being concatenated if placed at the end of the first one before delete-forward-char is called
Point-Char: |
Code: (lambda ()
       (php-mode)
       (call-interactively 'php-fill-delete-forward))
=-=
$stringVar = 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit |'
    . 'amet, consectetur.';
=-=
$stringVar = 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit |met, consectetur.';
=-=-=

Name: Stitches two string being concatenated if placed at the beginning of the last space
=-=
$stringVar = 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit| '
    . 'amet, consectetur.';
=-=
$stringVar = 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit|amet, consectetur.';
=-=-=

